{"tid":1613402,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我依家好撚憎差佬！對住差佬我會選擇放棄人性！","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:08:33.000Z","uid":14503,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"50d97cc309c952dd72e106499b605539e8f555e2","tid":1613402,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"我認我廢我唔夠膽私鳥你班仆街！<br />\n不過你都咪撚比我知你做差佬！<br />\n知你係差佬我一定見死不救！<br />\n因為我真係好撚憎恨你呢班香港差佬！你地唔撚係人！你地無人性！所以我決定對住你地唔會再講人性！！！<br />\n<br />\n人地仇恨你係你地自己攞黎！唔需要有人去散播仇恨大家有良心既都會對你地恨之入骨！！！<br />\n<br />\n我見你老婆穿洋水唔撚會幫你call白車！<br />\n我見到你比人搞唔撚會幫你做人證！<br />\n你問我借錢救命救你屋企人救你老豆老母我唔撚會借！<br />\n<br />\n你要人對你有人性咁你就離開警隊咪撚再做差佬！如果唔係我要你呢一世都怕比人知你係差佬！香港差佬係邪惡！做香港差佬係罪人！做香港差佬係恥辱！係抵撚死！係惹禍家人！係折福折壽！我屌你老母死班仆街死差佬！！！<br />\n<br />\n我發誓以後會對香港差佬見死不救！！！<br />\n<br />\nI WON&rsquo;T KILL YOU..BUT I DON&rsquo;T HAVE TO SAVE YOU!!!<br />\n<br />\n歡迎跟機！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JSCR92g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJSCR92g.jpg&h=5b502bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EjNEVj7CReY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEjNEVj7CReY&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=a0bf95d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EjNEVj7CReY</a>"},{"pid":"659c1db9f8b74582be7246634ce7dd7423680a7f","tid":1613402,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:08:04.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8e74e052d102f4f7982515afc6c1bd86318245e7","tid":1613402,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"d2a8a5f2210bd318251364a2d34303417dd76b35","tid":1613402,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"Push!!!"},{"pid":"70733e92f6fb1970ff2d712302ed3b5e48ba0066","tid":1613402,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:10:34.000Z","msg":"Push!!!"},{"pi